TRAVISWILD
This animal has earned a reputation in the dance music community as one of the most musically diverse, entertaining and energetic talent available. TRAVISWILD is known for his infectiously entertaining persona on stage and a loyal fan base affectionately referred to as 'The Animal Kingdom'. He has not only shared the stage with world renowned acts such as A-Trak, Thomas Jack, Chromeo, Ferry Corsten, Jeremy Olander, Fehrplay, Viceroy, & David Hohme but he is also the co-founder & resident DJ of "THE ANIMAL PARTY" which has sold out every showing in SF, NYC, Miami & The Hamptons. His 2016 tour includes stops in Tulúm, Whistler B.C., NYC, SF, Cartagena, Colombia & Miami where he sold out Wall twice as well as Marquee NY.
Traviswild.comSoundcloud
 
 
Aric Christopher
Truth seeker and nomadic spirit, Aric Christopher balances life's demands by seeking out to deliver a sound unique to its own. In his mixes you will discover shades of deep often tech house mixed in with elements of Nu Disco, while always keeping the vibe alive with driving funky bass lines. His sound is the product of a unique musical backround, which saw him as a young punk rock drummer, influenced heavily by underground hip hop and roots reggae. Aric has been Dj-ing all of the world as of late while simultaneously producing his own music from his home studio in Venice Beach. Lots to look forward to in this relentless happy realm of sound...
